quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,"Wɑkɑt ning sẽn Koagsd nebã sũyã!"
  101,2,"Wɑkɑt sẽn koagsd nebã sũyã yɑɑ bʋgo?"
  101,3,"La bõe n wildg foo koagsdã sẽn ya-a soaba?"
  101,4,"Yɑɑ raar ning nebã sẽn na n yɩ wala pilimpigd sẽn sãeege."
  101,5,"Tɩ tãnsã lebg wala Pʋmpʋm kõbd b sẽn yelg-ɑ."
  101,6,"Sã n yaa ned ning tʋʋm-sõng mɑgb sẽn zɩsgã."
  101,7,"Yẽnda bee vɩɩm pʋg b sẽn yard-ɑ."
  101,8,"La sã n yaa ned ning tʋʋm-sõms mɑgb sẽn yɩ faagɑ, tɩ wẽngã wil-ɑ."
  101,9,"Rẽnd yẽ gãag ziig yaa (hɑlkr lʋɩɩsẽ) Gεhɑnem pʋgẽ."
  101,10,"La bõe n wilgd foo bõe la yẽ?"
  101,11,"Yaa bug-tʋʋlga."
